                'current_conditions'   => 'Rhine near Duisburg, km 780. Channel depth 4.2m, vessel forward draft increasing (3.2m → 3.5m in 10 minutes, rising). Current 4 km/h. Dense traffic: push convoy 800m astern, passenger vessel 1,200m ahead approaching. Forepeak flooding, collision bulkhead deformed with cracks visible. Cargo tanks currently intact but hull damage near No. 1 tank boundary. Weather: daytime, good visibility. Duisburg port facilities 3 km ahead with crane facilities and pollution response capability. Bank depths 1.5-2.0m within 200m on both sides.',
